  "pageTitle": "面向再生骨料回收的破碎與篩分設備",
  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page product-page-industrial\"> <section class=\"section split-section\"> <div> <p class=\"eyebrow\">C&D 廢棄物回收</p> <h1>面向再生骨料回收的破碎與篩分設備</h1> <p class=\"hero-copy\">蔚澜 Lion One 系統結合破碎、滾筒骨料篩分、振動骨料篩分、磁性分離、氣流分離、打包、稱重及數位控制，涵蓋 C&D 廢棄物、裝飾廢棄物、拆除廢棄物及大型廢棄物專案。</p> <div class=\"hero-actions\"> <a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/contact\">請求提案</a></div></div> <picture> <img src=\"/assets/images/lion-mark1.jpg\" alt=\"綜合 C&D 廢棄物破碎與篩選站\"></picture></section> <section class=\"section\" id=\"core-parameters\" aria-labelledby=\"core-parameters-title\"> <div class=\"section-heading\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">核心資料</p> <h2 id=\"core-parameters-title\">Lion One 一體化站面向重載破碎、骨料篩分與分離</h2> <p>重型移動站設計用於建築、裝飾、拆除及大型廢棄物預處理應用。四個核心資料皆依其工作範圍列出。</p></div> <div class=\"spec-group spec-group-industrial\" aria-labelledby=\"core-parameters-title\"> <div class=\"spec-card-grid spec-card-grid-wide\"> <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-industrial\"> <header class=\"spec-card-head\"> <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">L1</span> <div class=\"spec-card-id\"> <p class=\"spec-card-model\">Lion One</p> <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">綜合破碎與篩選站</p></div> <dl class=\"spec-card-plate\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <div><dt>製造集團</dt><dd>蔚澜</dd></div> <div><dt>類型</dt><dd>移動站</dd></div> <div><dt>等級</dt><dd>重型&nbsp;</dd></div></dl></header> <dl class=\"spec-metrics spec-metrics-wide\"> <div class=\"spec-metric\"> <dt>處理能力</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">20&ndash;70</span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-suffix-unit\">t/h</span></dd></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\"> <dt>進料尺寸</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">200</span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-suffix-unit\">mm</span></dd></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\"> <dt>佔地面積</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">35</span><span class=\"spec-suffix\"><span class=\"spec-suffix-unit\">m<sup>2</sup></span> · 11.7 × 3 × 3.1 m</span></dd></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\"> <dt>驅動</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">100<small>%</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">全液壓</span></dd></div></dl> <footer class=\"spec-card-foot\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <span class=\"spec-card-foot-mark\">蔚澜</span> <span class=\"spec-card-foot-sep\"></span> <span>寧波，中國</span> <span class=\"spec-card-foot-sep\"></span> <span>整合移動站</span></footer></article></div></div></section> <section class=\"section\"> <div class=\"section-heading\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">工藝模組</p> <h2>回收效果由整合模組、液壓驅動與控制系統共同決定</h2> <p>配置用於回收骨料回收、輕質物料分離、金屬移除、自動化控制及作業報告。</p></div> <ol class=\"industrial-ledger\" role=\"list\"> <li class=\"industrial-ledger-row\"> <span class=\"industrial-ledger-tag\">M-01</span> <div class=\"industrial-ledger-body\"> <h3>一體化移動站</h3> <p>整合破碎與篩選站，具備200 mm穩定給料尺寸，35 m<sup>2</sup> 車身尺寸，並全液壓驅動。</p></div> <dl class=\"industrial-ledger-spec\"> <div><dt>穩定給料</dt><dd>200 mm</dd></div> <div><dt>驅動</dt><dd>液壓</dd></div></dl></li> <li class=\"industrial-ledger-row\"> <span class=\"industrial-ledger-tag\">M-02</span> <div class=\"industrial-ledger-body\"> <h3>產能範圍選項</h3> <p>處理能力選項適用於不同規模的市政、工業及 C&D 廢棄物資源化專案。</p></div> <dl class=\"industrial-ledger-spec\"> <div><dt>分布範圍</dt><dd>20-70 t/h</dd></div> <div><dt>分級</dt><dd>3 等級</dd></div></dl></li> <li class=\"industrial-ledger-row\"> <span class=\"industrial-ledger-tag\">M-03</span> <div class=\"industrial-ledger-body\"> <h3>模組化分離工段</h3> <p>覆蓋破碎機、C&D 廢棄物篩分、回收骨料振動篩、C&D 廢棄物磁性分離器、C&D 廢棄物正負壓氣流分離系統，以及打包機。</p></div> <dl class=\"industrial-ledger-spec\"> <div><dt>模組</dt><dd>6 階段</dd></div> <div><dt>設定</dt><dd>模組化</dd></div></dl></li> <li class=\"industrial-ledger-row\"> <span class=\"industrial-ledger-tag\">M-04</span> <div class=\"industrial-ledger-body\"> <h3>控制系統模式</h3> <p>手動、自動及遠端控制模式支援啟停控制、警示、稱重流量及報告。</p></div> <dl class=\"industrial-ledger-spec\"> <div><dt>模式</dt><dd>手動 · 自動 · 遠端</dd></div> <div><dt>控制</dt><dd>PLC + DCS</dd></div></dl></li></ol></section> <section class=\"section dark-section product-process-section\" aria-labelledby=\"construction-process-title\"> <div class=\"section-heading\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">工藝流程</p> <h2 id=\"construction-process-title\">工藝流程將混合 C&amp;D 廢棄物流轉化為可再利用骨料產出</h2> <p>C&D 廢棄物處理線透過受控的進料、破碎、篩選及最終回收處理，將混合的C&amp;D物料轉化為可重複使用的產出。</p></div> <div class=\"industrial-flow\" aria-label=\"骨料回收應用流程\"> <div class=\"industrial-flow-track\"> <article class=\"industrial-flow-node\"> <span class=\"industrial-flow-rank\">01</span> <h3>穩定給料</h3> <p>將建築、裝飾、拆除或大塊廢棄物送入整合處理線。</p> <figure class=\"industrial-flow-media\" aria-label=\"穩定給料影片佔位符\"> <div class=\"industrial-flow-video\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"影片即將推出\"> <span class=\"industrial-flow-video-tag\">CAM-01</span> <span class=\"industrial-flow-video-play\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span></div></figure></article> <article class=\"industrial-flow-node\"> <span class=\"industrial-flow-rank\">02</span> <h3>破碎</h3> <p>將混合廢棄物減少為較易管理的顆粒大小，以便下游篩選與分離。</p> <figure class=\"industrial-flow-media\" aria-label=\"破碎影片佔位符\"> <div class=\"industrial-flow-video\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"影片即將推出\"> <span class=\"industrial-flow-video-tag\">CAM-02</span> <span class=\"industrial-flow-video-play\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span></div></figure></article> <article class=\"industrial-flow-node\"> <span class=\"industrial-flow-rank\">03</span> <h3>骨料篩分</h3> <p>依尺寸分離材料至支援骨料回收及更乾淨的下游處理。</p> <figure class=\"industrial-flow-media\" aria-label=\"骨料篩分影片佔位符\"> <div class=\"industrial-flow-video\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"影片即將推出\"> <span class=\"industrial-flow-video-tag\">CAM-03</span> <span class=\"industrial-flow-video-play\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span></div></figure></article></div> <div class=\"industrial-flow-wrap\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <span class=\"industrial-flow-wrap-down\"></span> <span class=\"industrial-flow-wrap-arrow\"></span></div> <article class=\"industrial-flow-node industrial-flow-finale\"> <span class=\"industrial-flow-rank\">04</span> <p class=\"industrial-flow-finale-eyebrow\">產出</p> <h3>可再利用產出</h3> <p>生產回收骨料和可重複使用的組分，準備下游再利用。</p> <figure class=\"industrial-flow-media\" aria-label=\"回收輸出影像佔位符\"> <div class=\"industrial-flow-video\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"影片即將推出\"> <span class=\"industrial-flow-video-tag\">CAM-04</span> <span class=\"industrial-flow-video-play\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span></div></figure></article></div></section> <section class=\"section product-compare-section\" aria-labelledby=\"construction-compare-title\"> <div class=\"section-heading\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">對比資料</p> <h2 id=\"construction-compare-title\">對比資料覆蓋佔地、產能、功耗與安裝效率</h2> <p>蔚澜整合的C&amp;D廢棄物處理線如何與典型多機場址配置的對比，並以驅動總擁有成本的指標相比較。</p></div> <div class=\"product-compare-layout\"> <figure class=\"product-compare-explode\" aria-label=\"Lion One 爆炸視角\"> <div class=\"product-compare-explode-frame\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"爆炸視圖即將推出\"> <span class=\"product-compare-explode-tag\">爆炸 ·LION ONE</span> <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:18%;--pin-y:32%\" data-label=\"01\"></span> <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:38%;--pin-y:58%\" data-label=\"02\"></span> <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:58%;--pin-y:26%\" data-label=\"03\"></span> <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:74%;--pin-y:64%\" data-label=\"04\"></span> <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:88%;--pin-y:40%\" data-label=\"05\"></span> <span class=\"product-compare-explode-label\">爆炸視角即將登場</span></div> <figcaption> <span class=\"product-compare-explode-meta\">整合移動站 · 重型</span></figcaption></figure> <div class=\"product-compare-panel\"> <header class=\"product-compare-panel-head\"> <span class=\"product-compare-legend\"> <span class=\"product-compare-legend-mark is-self\"></span>蔚澜 Lion One</span> <span class=\"product-compare-legend\"> <span class=\"product-compare-legend-mark is-base\"></span>GREATWALL HAVEY INDUSTRY MK-F50</span></header> <ul class=\"product-compare-list\" role=\"list\"> <li class=\"product-compare-row\"> <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\"> <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-01</span> <h3>佔地面積</h3> <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">整合站的 m²</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bars\"> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:79%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">Lion One</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">35 m²</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:100%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">MK-F50</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">44.2 m²</span></div></div> <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">整合式移動站取代了單一滑架中的多機場佈局。</p></li> <li class=\"product-compare-row\"> <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\"> <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-02</span> <h3>處理能力</h3> <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">t/h額定範圍</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bars\"> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:100%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">Lion One</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">20-70 t/h</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:88.6%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">MK-F50</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">40-62 t/h</span></div></div> <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">處理能力條按 70 t/h 上限進行歸一化展示，標籤保留各型號的完整運行範圍。</p></li> <li class=\"product-compare-row\"> <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\"> <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-03</span> <h3>功耗</h3> <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">千瓦 / 100 t/h</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bars\"> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:80%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">Lion One</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">132 kW</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:100%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">MK-F50</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">165 kW</span></div></div> <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">按額定吞吐量計算，每噸分揀功率約降低25%。</p></li> <li class=\"product-compare-row\"> <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\"> <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-04</span> <h3>運輸與組裝</h3> <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">現場安裝天數</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bars\"> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:12%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">Lion One</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">2–3 天</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:95%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">MK-F50</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">18 – 25 天</span></div></div> <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">移動站使用標準拖車運輸；現場工作主要為定位與接駁。</p></li></ul></div></div></section> <section class=\"section industrial-faq-section\" aria-labelledby=\"construction-faq-title\"> <div class=\"section-heading\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">常見問題</p> <h2 id=\"construction-faq-title\">規模判斷從組成、進料尺寸、工藝模組與場地佈局開始</h2> <p>利用這些答案準備早期供應商比較、內部可行性紀錄及骨料回收應用設備的徵求條件（RFQ）資訊。</p></div> <div class=\"industrial-faq-panel\"> <article class=\"industrial-faq-item\"> <span class=\"industrial-faq-code\">RFQ-01</span> <div> <h3 class=\"industrial-faq-question\">成本與模組範圍</h3> <p class=\"industrial-faq-answer\">成本取決於產能需求、進料量、所需輸出、破碎與篩分範圍、磁性分離、氣流分離、打包、控制系統、場址配置及調試支援。</p> <div class=\"faq-input-list\"> <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需輸入</span> <span>產能依據</span> <span>場地配置</span></div></div></article> <article class=\"industrial-faq-item\"> <span class=\"industrial-faq-code\">RFQ-02</span> <div> <h3 class=\"industrial-faq-question\">可處理物料範圍</h3> <p class=\"industrial-faq-answer\">該處理線用於 C&D 廢棄物、裝飾廢棄物、拆除廢棄物、大塊廢棄物，以及需要破碎、骨料篩分、金屬回收和輕重分離的混合輕質物料。</p> <div class=\"faq-input-list\"> <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需輸入</span> <span>廢棄物組成</span> <span>物料照片或影片</span></div></div></article> <article class=\"industrial-faq-item\"> <span class=\"industrial-faq-code\">RFQ-03</span> <div> <h3 class=\"industrial-faq-question\">整合模組範圍</h3> <p class=\"industrial-faq-answer\">典型的生產線可能包括穩定給料、破碎、滾筒骨料篩分、振動骨料篩分、C&amp;D廢棄物磁性分離器、氣流分離系統、打包機、稱重、PLC 控制及遠端監控。</p> <div class=\"faq-input-list\"> <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需輸入</span> <span>所需輸出產品資料</span> <span>需要回收模組</span></div></div></article> <article class=\"industrial-faq-item\"> <span class=\"industrial-faq-code\">RFQ-04</span> <div> <h3 class=\"industrial-faq-question\">產能選擇依據</h3> <p class=\"industrial-faq-answer\">產能應與每小時來料量、物料密度、預期運行時間、產出資料、當地運輸節奏及場地佔地面積相匹配。蔚澜可以在建議20-70 t/h配置前先檢視專案資料。</p> <div class=\"faq-input-list\"> <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需輸入</span> <span>進料尺寸</span> <span>營運時間與運作時間</span></div></div></article></div></section> <section class=\"section industrial-rfq-section\" aria-labelledby=\"construction-rfq-title\"> <div class=\"section-heading\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">RFQ 輸入資料</p> <h2 id=\"construction-rfq-title\">配置精度取決於組成、進料尺寸、產能與佈局輸入</h2> <p>利用此清單準備足夠的工程背景，用於處理能力選擇、模組配置、運輸規劃及安裝評審。</p></div> <div class=\"industrial-rfq-checklist\"> <article> <span>DATA-01</span> <h3>廢棄物組成</h3> <p>估算混凝土、磚塊、木材、塑膠、金屬、土壤、裝飾廢棄物、大塊廢棄物及輕質雜質的比例。</p></article> <article> <span>DATA-02</span> <h3>進料尺寸</h3> <p>確認最大進貨尺寸、平均整塊大小、預分揀狀況，以及是否需要預先破碎的超大物料。</p></article> <article> <span>DATA-03</span> <h3>產能依據</h3> <p>分享每小時吞吐量、工作班次、預期運作時間、季節負載變動及最終總體產品資料。</p></article> <article> <span>DATA-04</span> <h3>場地配置</h3> <p>提供可用占地範圍、卡車動線、電力接入、用水與粉塵控制限制，以及出料儲存區。</p></article></div> <div class=\"rfq-action-strip\"> <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/contact\">請求工程評審流程</a> <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/resources\">準備檔案包</a></div></section></main>"
}
